data.description: Welcome to Modern living that is included with this Silvio model by Oakwood Homes in the beautiful community in Banning Lewis Ranch. This home offers a modern design that low-maintenance with an open design.  The open modern kitchen is a includes 42” upper cabinetry, stone counter tops and an extra large island that is not available in similar models. The ceramic tile back splash, stainless steel appliances and seating space at the island are perfect for family and small gatherings. On the upper level offers primary bedroom with lots natural light, and ensuite bathroom. The loft area between the primary and additional bedrooms offers multiple options. The upper level laundry room and the third bathroom offer the home owner additional convenience and quick access from all bedrooms. The two-car garage offers safe off the street parking and additional storage space. The additional amenities that the Banning Lewis Ranch area has to offer its residents, as well as quality school district make this home Must See Listing.
